## Verification
1. `npm run dev` and visually inspect every component
2. Test all 12 tools are 1-click accessible in the toolbar
3. Test view mode switching (segmented control)
4. Test toggle states (grid, snap, sidebar, properties)
5. Test Save dirty indicator, undo/redo disabled states
6. Test sidebar: floor card hover actions, section collapse, add buttons, object selection
7. Test properties panel: unit toggle, color picker, delete/action buttons, export menu
8. Test modal: open/close, escape key, overlay click, load/delete project
9. Test responsive: resize below 1100px and 900px breakpoints
10. Verify no regressions in keyboard shortcuts (V/W/D/N/etc., Ctrl+Z/S)
